send_employee.comment_client: From your candidates, the only interesting option at this point was Irina H, because she knows Figma (which we use a lot), and states to have experience with content plan, sales and advertising strategy. So if you want to have a shorter call, I could just ask her if she could help me out drafting the content strategy for my revamped website.

need_candidates.comment_requirements:
I will need help in the following order: 

- content strategy

- content creation

- content structuring

- wireframing

- reachout plan that align with landing pages and target market

- Sales/chat help

- LinkedIn implementation in the long term


I have a good project manager, communications manager, and reliable developers. But I lack sales/lead generation implementation and support.


I understand that I will have to take as much charge of the sales as I can personally, but I would need a sidekick to the entire implementation process. Both in big picture, and smaller details.


If we can nail the first 2 months, I'm happy to collaborate full time as long as all parties are happy with how things work out together.
